1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 27=

3
00:00:53,039 --> 00:00:53,880
It was her!

4
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:55,759
She's the one who said it!

5
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:58,039
She said your mother-in-law is very rich

6
00:00:58,039 --> 00:00:59,119
and loves to show it off.

7
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,560
She hates your mother-in-law.

8
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,479
So she asked me
to set up this scheme with her.

9
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:03,359
It was her.

10
00:01:04,119 --> 00:01:04,679
Qian Hongyan!

11
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:06,119
You lowlife!

12
00:01:06,679 --> 00:01:08,079
You actually set me up to scam me?

13
00:01:08,759 --> 00:01:09,719
She's lying!

14
00:01:10,010 --> 00:01:11,560
She was the one who came to me first!

15
00:01:11,879 --> 00:01:12,480
She told me

16
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:13,959
to lure you into the trap.

17
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,640
She'd already had her eye on you.

18
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,320
You lied to me, didn't you?

19
00:01:17,599 --> 00:01:18,439
You lied to me!

20
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,760
Come out now!

21
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,439
Come out!

22
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:22,640
You lied to me!

23
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,480
You lied to me!

24
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,159
Mom! Mom!

25
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:24,840
Qian Hongyan, you liar!

26
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,439
Stop it!

27
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:27,079
Take her back to our house first.

28
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,159
I'll deal with her later.

29
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,319
Get up!

30
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,120
Get up!

31
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,519
Move!

32
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,990
Now that no one else is here,

33
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,560
let's talk about the USB drive.

34
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,120
Who sent you?

35
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,280
I... I don't know.

36
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:50,920
I don't know!

37
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,500
-Talk!
- The money came

38
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:54,000
from an overseas account.

39
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:56,120
They paid me to set up this scheme.

40
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,719
(Another overseas account...)

41
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,879
Ms. Lan, I was wrong!

42
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,680
Please forgive me!

43
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,239
Please forgive me, Ms. Lan!

44
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:10,599
Changkun, I was blinded by greed.

45
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:12,760
Please don't hold it against me!

46
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,280
I'm begging you. Please let me go!

47
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,400
Churan, you're the most sensible one,

48
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,120
the kindest one.

49
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,759
Please say a few words for me.

50
00:02:22,262 --> 00:02:23,862
You liar!

51
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:26,039
And you still have the nerve to cry?

52
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:28,759
Why...

53
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,039
Why are you all looking at me?

54
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:30,950
Alright, I was wrong, okay?

55
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,439
I...

56
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:32,759
They tricked me into it!

57
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:35,290
If you weren't so greedy,
could they have tricked you?

58
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:35,960
I...

59
00:02:36,719 --> 00:02:37,159
I...

60
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:39,360
I don't know what came over me.

61
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,039
Mom,

62
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,719
Ye Chen already has it hard enough.

63
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:43,960
Please stop making things harder for him.

64
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,840
You can't blame Mom entirely either.

65
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,137
Their real target was me.

66
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,439
Chen, you're the best.

67
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,879
Can you tell me what's
on that USB drive?

68
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:53,280
Is it very valuable?

69
00:02:54,325 --> 00:02:55,648
Both yes and no.

70
00:02:56,125 --> 00:02:57,460
It's just some commercial secrets.

71
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,625
Mr. Qin asked me
to keep it safe for him.

72
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:00,275
Ye Chen,

73
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,319
I was wrong!

74
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:03,639
Please let me go! Please forgive me!

75
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:05,120
Let me ask you one thing.

76
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:08,520
Did the rest
of the Xiao family know about this?

77
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,479
Did the scam work?

78
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,990
Did you take the photos?

79
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:15,520
Did you get the villa?

80
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,879
Did Ye Chen cry?

81
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,759
They called the police!

82
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,560
They're going to send me to jail!

83
00:03:21,570 --> 00:03:22,520
I don't want to go to jail!

84
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,520
Xiao Changqian!

85
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,240
Save me please!

86
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,879
That's enough already.

87
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:28,719
Why call the police?

88
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,159
I'll beat some sense into you!

89
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:32,199
You hit me?

90
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,319
So what if I did?

91
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,520
I'm your uncle.

92
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:36,639
If you pull this kind of stunt again,

93
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:37,360
I'll slap you again.

94
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,199
But you didn't really lose anyth...

95
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:41,080
Do you even hear yourself?

96
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,680
Xiao Changkun!

97
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:45,290
Have you lost your mind?

98
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:47,919
How dare you hit my children?

99
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,879
I'm telling you!

100
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,879
If you won't discipline them, then I will!

101
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,360
I...

102
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,479
Come on!

103
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:53,759
Hit me.

104
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:54,879
Go on.

105
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:55,800
Hit me again.

106
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,390
Come on.

107
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:57,400
I...

108
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,520
Let me tell you.

109
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:01,199
if you don't teach your kids,
someone else will have to.

110
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:04,319
Look at the state our family is in now.

111
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:06,439
It's a disgrace.

112
00:04:08,212 --> 00:04:09,840
Are you even still my elder brother?

113
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:13,450
When we were kids,
you treated me so well.

114
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:16,960
You saved my life.

115
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:19,937
I nearly drowned
when I went fishing in the river,

116
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,770
and you were the one
who saved me, remember?

117
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:22,319
Right?

118
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,879
But look at you now.

119
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,325
Your hand is raised,
like you're going to hit me.

120
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:28,987
Are you really my brother?

121
00:04:30,125 --> 00:04:32,160
Are you really my brother?

122
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,199
Enough!

123
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,560
Hongyan may be at fault,

124
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,120
but you were unfilial first.

125
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,300
What's all this fighting for?

126
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,560
We're all family here.

127
00:04:43,959 --> 00:04:45,600
I've never felt like we were family!

128
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:49,199
Who here ever treated me like family?

129
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:51,360
Mom,

130
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,920
you've looked down on me
since I was a child.

131
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,360
You never respected me.

132
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,399
You thought I was stupid, useless,

133
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,839
and that I wasn't cunning enough!

134
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:03,600
After Father died,

135
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,480
you got even worse.

136
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,512
You drove my family out
of the ancestral house.

137
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:12,120
And later, when Changqian
bullied me again and again,

138
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,600
did you ever stop him?

139
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,480
Are you really my mother?

140
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:21,639
Let me tell you,

141
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,720
you're the one most responsible

142
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:27,240
for the state our family is in now.

143
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,790
Family scandals
shouldn't be aired in public.

144
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,160
Xiao Group

145
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,399
is still under my control.

146
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,190
If you keep making trouble,

147
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:35,279
then Xiao Churan

148
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,439
can forget about staying chairwoman.

149
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,160
Fine.

150
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,800
Then I won't

151
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,600
be chairwoman anymore.

152
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:51,920
Ye Chen,

153
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:54,160
you jinx!

154
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:55,287
Look at what you've done!

155
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:57,160
Look what you've

156
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:59,120
turned the Xiao family into!

157
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:01,360
Weren't you the ones
who always called me trash?

158
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,720
Called me useless?

159
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,560
So why do you think so highly of me now?

160
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,720
To be honest,
I've always disliked you all.

161
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,850
But at the same time,
I'm grateful to you all.

162
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,800
If it weren't for you all,

163
00:06:13,810 --> 00:06:15,580
I wouldn't have married
into the Xiao family.

164
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:17,360
I wouldn't have met kind-hearted Churan,

165
00:06:19,237 --> 00:06:20,341
upright Dad,

166
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,240
and Mom, who can be vain

167
00:06:26,037 --> 00:06:27,810
and greedy at times,
but with a good heart.

168
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,400
We are the real family.

169
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:33,160
And I won't allow any outsider

170
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,800
to bully my family.

171
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:44,560
What do we do?

172
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:45,920
The police are here.

173
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,519
Who sent that scammer?

174
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:50,639
I've already asked Song Wanting
to track that overseas account.

175
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,839
At the same time, I've asked Kun

176
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,880
to investigate the phone number
that directed him.

177
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,839
Whoever is behind this,

178
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,480
the truth will come out soon.

179
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,680
Trying to mess with me won't be so easy.

180
00:07:02,462 --> 00:07:03,869
What I'm worried about is you all.

181
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,279
Just look, Mom got dragged into this too.

182
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:08,560
I've already talked with her properly.

183
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,079
After this,

184
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,360
she'll definitely change.

185
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,839
Qian Hongyan is involved
in a major fraud case.

186
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,690
She'll be in prison
for at least several years.

187
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:21,320
Old Mrs. Xiao and the others
weren't directly involved,

188
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:22,990
but they've been detained
for a few days.

189
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,279
They'll be released soon.

190
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:28,920
But no matter who it is,

191
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:32,879
anyone who dares to touch my family
will pay the price.

192
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,980
(Lawyer's Letter)
On behalf of Dihao Group,

193
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:41,950
I hereby formally notify you.

194
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,337
Dihao Group has decided

195
00:07:43,337 --> 00:07:45,217
to terminate all cooperation
with Xiao Group.

196
00:07:45,637 --> 00:07:46,560
(Lawyer's Letter)
Huaying Pharma

197
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,360
has also decided

198
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,360
to terminate all cooperation
with Xiao Group.

199
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,560
Song Group
will never have any business dealings

200
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,850
with Xiao Group too.

201
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,680
(New Xiao Group)
Congratulations, Ms. Xiao!

202
00:08:02,962 --> 00:08:03,720
(Grand Opening)

203
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,480
Congratulations!

204
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,850
- Thank you, Mr. Hao!
- Thank you.

205
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:06,759
Please, come inside!

206
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,720
Congratulations, Ms. Xiao and Mr. Ye.

207
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,360
Thank you.

208
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:14,560
Congratulations, Churan.

209
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,319
Dihao will give you our full support.

210
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,519
Thank you, Ms. Wang.

211
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:19,839
Thank you.

212
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:28,920
Madam, congratulations.
Happy grand opening.

213
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:30,120
(Super Red Envelope)
Here's a gift.

214
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:30,959
Thank you.

215
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:31,680
My dad also said,

216
00:08:31,690 --> 00:08:34,590
if any of our projects interest you,
feel free to pick whichever you like.

217
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:37,079
Congratulations, Mr. Ye.

218
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,390
Thank you, Ms. Song.

219
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,120
Ms. Song,

220
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,159
my madam's company just opened,

221
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,780
and you're only congratulating
my master?

222
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,320
My apologies.

223
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:45,519
I've been rude.

224
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,638
Congratulations to you as well,
Ms. Xiao.

225
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,487
Miss Xiao?

226
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,279
Shouldn't you call her Mrs. Ye?

227
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,039
It's alright,  Ms. Song.

228
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,559
Thank you.

229
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,559
Churan, go greet the guests.

230
00:08:56,637 --> 00:08:58,180
- I need to talk to  Ms. Song.
- Okay.

231
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,519
- Please, this way.
- Alright.

232
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:02,200
Smooth sailing and prosperity.

233
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:05,840
The three accounts you gave me

234
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,880
were routed through multiple layers
of a Myanmar scam network.

235
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:12,399
They were transferred many times,
taking countless detours.

236
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,720
After comparing all the transactions,

237
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,370
we finally traced the original source
of the funds

238
00:09:16,387 --> 00:09:18,959
to an offshore company registered
in the Cayman Islands.

239
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:22,279
And the actual controlling shareholder
behind that company is...

240
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,162
Tang Sihai.

241
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,000
Looks like you already
have your suspicions.

242
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,890
Haven't you always had a partnership
with Dihao?

243
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,720
Why would Tang Sihai...

244
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,759
It's a long story.

245
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:33,990
Hard to explain in a few words.

246
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:35,159
Do you need my help?

247
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,320
Actually, there is something
I could use your help with.

248
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:40,919
Sure.

249
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:42,600
But once it's done,

250
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,919
you must join Song Group

251
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,279
as our Chief Appraiser.

252
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,812
Have you found out
who's using the phone number

253
00:09:54,812 --> 00:09:56,280
that instructed He Lian
to set up the trap?

254
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,559
Not yet.

255
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:58,759
Give me a little more time.

256
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,590
We've been friends for years.
I know you too well.

257
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,990
Does it have something
to do with Wang Dongxue?

258
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:09,519
That phone number

259
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:11,799
is indeed registered
under Dongxue's name.

260
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,639
But I'm sure
there must be some misunderstanding.

261
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:17,480
Dongxue is such a good person.

262
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,936
There's no way
she'd do something like this.

263
00:10:18,937 --> 00:10:20,399
Even if she did,

264
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:22,080
I'm sure Tang Sihai
was the one behind it.

265
00:10:23,425 --> 00:10:24,960
You can't blame Dongxue entirely.

266
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:27,840
Daokun,

267
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,000
we're best friends.

268
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,440
I won't force you.

269
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,240
Cut the nonsense.

270
00:10:41,650 --> 00:10:42,770
We're best friends for life.

271
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:51,037
(Hired killer to stage a car crash.
Obsessed with the formula)

272
00:10:51,037 --> 00:10:52,325
(The mastermind)

273
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:57,612
(Hired killer to stage a car crash.
Killed Madam Li)

274
00:10:58,780 --> 00:10:59,540
(Old Mr. Xiao kept one copy
of the formula)

275
00:10:59,540 --> 00:11:00,660
(Cooperate with the Xiao family
under Tang Sihai's orders.)

276
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,960
I knew I'd find you here.

277
00:11:12,137 --> 00:11:14,000
(The mastermind)

278
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:16,120
Are you sure?

279
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:18,290
We're still waiting
for Song Wanting's confirmation.

280
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,159
What are you going to do next?

281
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,320
Revenge.

282
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:30,000
Mr. Tang, have a drink.

283
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:30,879
Excuse me.

284
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,660
Ms. Song, if you have something to say,
just say it.

285
00:11:34,475 --> 00:11:36,181
I'd like to make a deal with you, sir.

286
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,200
Go on.

287
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,559
Hand Ye Chen over to me.

288
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,675
You can't handle him anyway.

289
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,279
And you think you can handle him?

290
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:45,279
I could try.

291
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,320
Nothing.

292
00:12:28,559 --> 00:12:29,480
There's nothing.

293
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:31,559
See? I told you
there must be some misunderstanding.

294
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,400
Think about it again.

295
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,000
Ye Chen is mine.

296
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,840
No one is taking him away.

297
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,480
Let me offer you a piece of advice,
Ms. Song.

298
00:13:10,612 --> 00:13:14,060
Some games are not something
you should casually step into.

299
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,600
This is bigger than you can handle.

300
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,600
Thank you for the concern, Mr. Tang.

301
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,240
But I'm already

302
00:13:23,879 --> 00:13:25,559
in the game.

303
00:13:49,687 --> 00:13:52,175
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

304
00:13:52,262 --> 00:13:56,015
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

305
00:13:56,475 --> 00:14:01,412
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

306
00:14:01,575 --> 00:14:03,862
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

307
00:14:04,175 --> 00:14:06,855
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

308
00:14:07,925 --> 00:14:10,550
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

309
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:13,862
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

310
00:14:14,062 --> 00:14:17,112
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

311
00:14:17,225 --> 00:14:20,187
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

312
00:14:20,455 --> 00:14:23,612
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

313
00:14:23,837 --> 00:14:27,587
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

314
00:14:27,587 --> 00:14:30,450
♪I belong to no one♪

315
00:14:30,512 --> 00:14:33,962
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

316
00:14:33,962 --> 00:14:36,637
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

317
00:14:36,637 --> 00:14:42,975
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
